          <h2 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">中国特色社会主义如何探路而来 - 读《筚路维艰》</h2>
        

        <div class="post-meta">
          <span class="post-time">
            
              <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
                <i class="fa fa-calendar-o"></i>
              </span>
              
                <span class="post-meta-item-text">Posted on</span>
              
              <time title="Post created" itemprop="dateCreated datePublished" datetime="2022-12-03T21:20:44+08:00">
                2022-12-03
              </time>
            

            

            
          </span>

          
            <span class="post-category" >
            
              <span class="post-meta-divider">|</span>
            
